## Tier 3 — 🏗️ Infrastructure & Backend Quality

### 3.1 — Streaming AI Responses (SSE)
**What**: Currently, AI responses (roadmap generation, tutor chat) likely wait for the full response before rendering. Use Server-Sent Events (SSE) to stream tokens as they arrive.
- Works for roadmap generation, tutor chat, and mock interview.
- Frontend shows a typing animation as the AI responds.
- **Impact**: Makes the AI feel dramatically faster and more natural.

