## Verification Plan

### Per Feature
- Each new page will be manually tested in the browser.
- Each new API endpoint will have a corresponding test in `backend/tests/`.
- AI features will be validated with prompt injection and edge case inputs.

### Overall
- Run `node scripts/dbBenchmark.js` before and after Tier 3 changes to confirm no performance regressions.
- Run Lighthouse audit on the frontend before and after Tier 1/4 UI changes.
- Run `axe-core` accessibility audit after Tier 4 changes.
